== Events == === [[Fragmented Wastes]] (sky) === ;[[Fragmented Wastes (meta event)|Fragmented Wastes meta event]] This is a continuous series of events on the shattered top layer of Bloodstone Fen. Rifts open and expunge disorientated creatures that must be beaten down to force them back into the rift. When enough creatures have been defeated, the rift closes and the event succeeds.
Rifts can be reached from the air, or via Rift Entrances that spawn in the [[Haunted Canyons]] and [[Bloodstone Maw]] areas. Once eight of these rifts are closed, a group boss event will spawn at [[Bloodstone's Shell]]. * {{event|Defeat beasts disgorged from the blazing unstable rift}} * {{event|Defeat beasts disgorged from the frigid unstable rift}} * {{event|Defeat beasts disgorged from the rumbling unstable rift}} ** {{event|Defeat the enormous bloodstone elemental!}}
;[[Colosseum of the Faithful]] event chain * {{event|Exorcise the angered spirits haunting Zealot's Overlook}} ** {{event|Defeat the spirit of Justiciar Hablion}} <small>(This chain is on a similar timer to [[Bloodstone Maw (meta event)|Bloodstone Maw meta event]]. It resets 30 minutes after [[Ghostly Justiciar Hablion]] is defeated.)</small>
=== [[Haunted Canyons]] (west / ground) === ;[[The spirits mostly come out at night. Mostly...]] During the day, there will be two occasional events and a large number of [[White Mantle]] in the area. Once [[Day and night|night falls]], the meta chain begins with an exorcism event to eliminate disturbed ghosts. Once completed, four Champion ghosts will spawn after one another and finally an escort event with [[Alari Doubleblade]] as she makes her way to [[Tomb of the Confessors]]. ; Day events * {{event|Defeat the patrolling justiciar}} * {{event|Defeat the patrolling crazed agent}} ; Night events * {{event|Exorcise the angered spirits stalking the Haunted Canyons}} ** {{event|Defeat the angry spirit of Savant Ehrin}} *** {{event|Defeat the angry spirit of Nyle the Compassionate}} **** {{event|Defeat the angry spirit of Ritualist Josa}} ***** {{event|Defeat the angry spirit of Thief Lloyd}} ****** {{event|Escort Alari Doubleblade on her quest for vengeance}}
;Other events * {{event|Kill the seekers to halt the cleric's supply of bloodstone shards, or throw shards at her to weaken her shield}} ** {{event|Kill the White Mantle cleric!}} ** {{event|Kill the empowered White Mantle cleric!}} * {{event|Find and slay the treasure mushroom! (Bloodstone Fen)}} * {{event|Stop the skritt burglar before she escapes with the treasure}}
=== [[Bloodstone Maw]] (east / depths) === ;[[Bloodstone Maw (meta event)|Bloodstone Maw meta event]] The meta event approximately on a 60-90 minute cooldown, the timer appears to be instance-based rather than set on a global timer. The countdown starts when the Unbound Guardian dies or an event in the event chain fails. After the countdown, the Jade Construct events will recommence. The first event of the chain starts at the {{waypoint|Ground Zero Waypoint}}. A [[Champion Jade Armor]] or a [[Champion Jade Bow]] must be defeated before it absorbs the [[Bloodstone Stalagmite]] (which can be communed with for experience and 10 Unbound Magic once the Jade Construct is dead). Once the first event has been completed, a new one will appear at the lower level, followed by two more of the same format. The final event of this type features both the Armor and the Bow bosses.
After all of the Jade bosses have been defeated, a [[Legendary Unbound Guardian]] appears deep within the [[Cavern of Unseen Lights]]. A time limit of 15 minutes is in place to defeat it. * {{event|Defeat the jade construct before it drains the bloodstone!}} (occurs four times in different locations) ** {{event|Defeat the jade constructs before they drain the bloodstone!}} *** {{event|Disperse the Unbound Guardian}}
