== Trivia == {{gww}} * During the events of ''[[Guild Wars]]'', the [[White Mantle]] would use this location to sacrifice villagers at the behest of the [[mursaat]] in order to power the [[gw1:soul battery|soul batteries]] keeping shut the [[gw1:Door of Komalie|Door of Komalie]].
